Author: VeryEmbarresingAlt
Text: FORREAL   I didn't eat for 2 days besides a few pieces of potato (restrict into a fast), but went to the gym, come back, my mom says "oh you're looking slimmer" like what it's been 2 days and my BMI is shit and I lost a pound at most, what are you on?  Parents really always tryna get you to eat smh
